title: Lindsey Williams - The Next 12 Months - DVD - American_Tradition
description:
What is going to happen in the next 12 months? Do you know? Do you care? What if the economy was going to collapse? What if the prices of oil and the stability of the US dollar were controlled by a few elite, power hungry people waiting to mop up after the financial ruin of America?

Find out by watching the Next 12 Months and listening to the hours of extra interviews included on the disk. Get involved and warn people about the upcoming depression that will leave this nation in a state of turmoil much like that of the 1929 depression, or maybe even worse!
